        M120,80 h20 v10 h-20 z
        M20,90 h120 v10 h-120 z
        M10,100 h140 v40 h-140 z
        M30,140 h20 v10 h-20 z
        M120,140 h20 v10 h-20 z"/>

    <!-- Hood inner shadow #004D40 -->
